-space: pre-wrap; font-stretch: normal; font-size: medium; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Î¢ÈíÑÅºÚ, Arial, sans-serif; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">\r\n	靓丽的(AUQA)水蓝色带着充满活力的运动或冲浪气息。速品蓝可以说最近才流行起来的，时尚而清新的色彩绝对是流行的不二之选，富有清新海洋之色的速品蓝也不负众望，为家居的陈设带来了一股清新的微风，感觉像是漫步在希腊的街头，张开双臂就可以拥抱海风啦。</p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 27px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); max-width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; font-stretch: normal; font-size: medium; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Î¢ÈíÑÅºÚ, Arial, sans-serif; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">\r\n	<img alt=\"640.webp.jpg\" src=\"http://xz.hxpwzs.com/huaxun/upload/image/20150112/1421042420425006.jpg\" style=\"border: medium none;\" title=\"1421042420425006.jpg\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 27px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); max-width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; font-stretch: normal; font-size: medium; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Î¢ÈíÑÅºÚ, Arial, sans-serif; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; max-width: 100%; border-bottom-color: rgb(255, 122, 0); border-bottom-width: 2px; border-bottom-style: solid; float: left; padding: 0px 2px 3px; text-align: justify; margin: 0px; orphans: 2; widows: 2; display: block; line-height: 28px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-width: 100%; padding: 4px 10px; margin: 0px 8px 0px 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 122, 0);\">2</span><strong style=\"max-width: 100%; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; line-height: 24px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">西柚</strong></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 27px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); max-width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; font-stretch: normal; font-size: medium; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Î¢ÈíÑÅºÚ, Arial, sans-serif; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">\r\n	西柚作为一种新的色彩出现在米兰的秀场上，让它在2015年中的表现不容忽视。西柚色的特色之处就在于它及其富有表现力的红色，不似粉色腻人，也不似大红闪耀，多了一股知性和优雅，同时还拥有了一股少女的气息。</p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 27px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); max-width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; font-stretch: normal; font-size: medium; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Î¢ÈíÑÅºÚ, Arial, sans-serif; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">\r\n	<img alt=\"641.webp.jpg\" src=\"http://xz.hxpwzs.com/huaxun/upload/image/20150112/1421042442479851.jpg\" style=\"border: medium none;\" title=\"1421042442479851.jpg\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 27px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); max-width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; font-stretch: normal; font-size: medium; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Î¢ÈíÑÅºÚ, Arial, sans-serif; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; max-width: 100%; border-bottom-color: rgb(255, 122, 0); border-bottom-width: 2px; border-bottom-style: solid; float: left; padding: 0px 2px 3px; text-align: justify; margin: 0px; orphans: 2; widows: 2; display: block; line-height: 28px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-width: 100%; padding: 4px 10px; margin: 0px 8px 0px 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 122, 0);\">3</span><strong style=\"max-width: 100%; padding: 0px; marg